'''Ceramacrete''' was a hard substance used to pave roads. The streets on [[Naos III/Legends|Naos III]] were mostly damaged ceramacrete paving. The turbolift shaft below the lower levels of the [[500 Republica/Legends|500 Republica]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] was made from ancient, cracked ceramacrete.<ref name="LoE">''[[Labyrinth of Evil]]''</ref> The floors of the [[Separatist communications facility]] on [[Jaguada's moon]] were made from ceramacrete.<ref name="DL">''[[Dark Lord: The Rise of Darth Vader]]''</ref>

